WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Welcome to this video demonstration

00:00:03.500 --> 00:00:07.000
This is a custom HTML5 video player

00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:11.000
With advanced features and controls

00:00:11.500 --> 00:00:15.000
Including subtitle support in multiple languages

00:00:15.500 --> 00:00:19.000
You can toggle subtitles on and off

00:00:19.500 --> 00:00:23.000
Or switch between different languages

00:00:23.500 --> 00:00:27.000
The video player also supports quality selection

00:00:27.500 --> 00:00:31.000
Variable playback speeds

00:00:31.500 --> 00:00:35.000
Picture-in-picture mode

00:00:35.500 --> 00:00:39.000
And fullscreen viewing

00:00:39.500 --> 00:00:43.000
Keyboard shortcuts are available too

00:00:43.500 --> 00:00:47.000
Press spacebar to play or pause

00:00:47.500 --> 00:00:51.000
Use arrow keys to seek and adjust volume

00:00:51.500 --> 00:00:55.000
Thanks for watching!
